Information
------------------------------

Experience the excitement and terror of nature's most awesome power from the safety of your home. Join expert storm chasers, scientists and amateur videocam owners as they capture the incredible fury of Twisters! This spectacular two-tape documentary puts you in the path of deadly tornadoes with their house-smashing, tree-snapping and car-throwing energy. Volume One features the scientists of &quot;Project Vortex&quot; as they place their instruments around killer tornadoes. Also follow along with some leading storm chasers and view their best video sequences on dangerous cyclones. Volume Two features the most incredible twister action ever captured by amateurs. Witness terrifying escapes as homeowners run for cover and see the horrible damage left behind by the most powerful tornadoes. Also features a countdown of the top ten most destructive tornado video sequences. The action is non-stop so let your VCR put you in the path of the Twisters!

